    "body": "## Scope\n\nConnector-authored recovery for the Safari-confirmed dev-check boot failure blocking Boomer Step 4.4B registration.\n\nExact baseline: `1548aae817f700c98208e8b7051b58babdeb2fe2`.\n\nChanged paths only:\n- `AsyncScene/Web/index.html`\n- `docs/index.html`\n\nThe two mirrors are byte-identical (`cc8a05355d441fa75a01dd22aabdb159382d76d6`).\n\n## Root cause\n\nThe deployed `dev-checks.js` aborts in the late `installZoomerShorteningDocsSmoke()` path because `getZoomerShorteningDocsBootSmokeRegistry` is referenced outside the earlier lexical scope where it was introduced. The authoritative Step 2.6 smoke functions have already been exported to `Game.__DEV` / `Game.Dev` before that late installer runs.\n\n## Recovery\n\nDefine a fail-closed global resolver before deferred `dev-checks.js` execution. It reconstructs the historical registry contract from the already-exported authoritative public stores and still throws `ReferenceError` if any required Step 2.6 export is genuinely absent. The dev-check cache-bust advances to `step6_boomer_4_4b_dev_checks_boot_registration_recovery_20260722b`.\n\nNo product copy, gameplay, economy, state, persistence, battle, NPC, or `dev-checks.js` source semantics are changed.\n\nA separately preserved local source-level implementation exists at local-only commit `54f0e7eaf2efbb1eee6499d0abe937fa79c5e5c7`, but local Git transport repeatedly failed with `Recv failure: Connection reset by peer`; this PR is an independently authored remote recovery and does not claim to be that exact commit.\n\nSafari acceptance remains `PENDING_USER` and will be rerun after integration.",
    "changed_files": 2,
